{"tid":1005880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（自古以來）明朝艦隊曾抵達澳洲大陸？西澳疑似發現明代佛像","createTime":"2019-02-02T14:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T03:57:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5a6025ecf62b6383a09cc44e5e74b90cbd1dff","tid":1005880,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"近日，兩名澳大利亞男子在西澳大利亞州用金屬探測器發現了一尊青銅佛像。這尊嬰兒佛像是在拍攝考古紀錄片時被發現的。目前，澳方已聯繫中國駐澳大使館，相關專家也正在研究該佛像的起源。據澳媒報導，這尊佛像或可證明1421年中國明朝的「尋寶艦隊」曾來澳大利亞探索過，該時間比歐洲人抵達澳大利亞早了200多年，如果屬實則可能會改寫目前已知的澳大利亞歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190202/29938818.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F29938818.html&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=01c0f473\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190202/29938818.html</a>"},{"pid":"f3bbb2f5f25acd9c2e608e290992aa456f8489d9","tid":1005880,"uid":58335,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"西澳大利亞州自古以來是屬於中國，是不可分割的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2ee683f1edb532ab5f8a9f8f9b5b70d39eea69","tid":1005880,"uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"上星期支那狗自己埋落去咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da30f0c2a300b8076ded0d19b92f3b93fdb27e2f","tid":1005880,"uid":55493,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"木箱漂流都有可能嘅，不過太多資料要查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳洲野味，正"},{"pid":"7db40facae1e0c2536b2ee00ac9f29a351a57c95","tid":1005880,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"新浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead